{"type":null,"faqId":44120,"title":"闪光灯无法使用如何解决？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.21875in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.875in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.70902777in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 请切换闪光灯模式为强制闪光灯模式</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156221\" style=\"width:0.30555555in;height:0.22361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">，拍照或录像时将始终打开闪光灯。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 若开启了闪光灯自动模式</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=156222\" style=\"width:0.30555555in;height:0.22361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">，相机将会根据环境光强度自动开启或关闭闪光灯。若要在光线充足的环境下使用闪光灯，请开启强制闪光灯模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 请确认手机是否正在充电，部分手机在充电时无法使用闪光灯，请拔掉充电器后尝试是否可以正常使用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 请确认手机电池电量是否充足。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">为延长手机的使用时间，当电池电量过低时，系统会自动禁止使用闪光灯。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">为保证手机正常使用，请及时为手机充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手机过热或闪光灯使用过于频繁，导致闪光灯温度过高时可能无法使用闪光灯，请过一段时间后重试。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">请确认您是否您使用了一些扫码软件，导致闪光灯无法使用。请您关闭扫描软件后再开启闪光灯。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9620","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400098000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"闪光灯,无法使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}